div.div:
Port Management System
«system»
Comprehensive port operations management system
Key Capabilities:
• Vessel and vessel type management
• Vessel Visit Notification (VVN) management
• Organization and resource management
• Dock and storage area management
• 3D port visualization (Three.js)
• User authentication (Google OAuth)
• Scheduling and planning (Prolog)
Technology Stack:
• Frontend: Angular 20 + Three.js
• Backend: .NET 9.0 + ASP.NET Core
• Database: SQL Server
• Auth: Google OAuth 2.0 + JWT
